I created this infographic using Canva to explain the concept of digital literacy in a simple and visual way.
The design covers important topics such as the meaning of digital literacy, useful tools for students, safe internet practices, 
professional online presence, and email etiquette. I used icons, colors, and short bullet points to make the content easy to understand and visually appealing. 
The aim of this infographic is to help students quickly learn how to use digital tools responsibly and maintain a safe and professional presence online.
